                        <h3><a href="#">Clinical Algorithm(s)</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>The following algorithms are provided in the original guideline document:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
    <li>An example of a pulmonary nodule service pathway </li>
    <li>Initial approach to solid pulmonary nodules </li>
    <li>Solid pulmonary nodule surveillance algorithm </li>
    <li>Sub-solid pulmonary nodules algorithm </li>
    <li>Pulmonary nodule treatment algorithm </li>
</ul></div></p>

